{"abstract":[{"text":"Pass data from child views up to their ancestors.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Guides","generated":true,"anchor":"Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/StateManagement","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/ThemingGuide","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/FocusSystem","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/StatusBarGuide","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/AppearanceAndColors","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/CustomViews","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/KeyboardShortcuts","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/PaletteReference","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/ListAndTable","doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/LayoutSystem"]}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Protocols","anchor":"Protocols","identifiers":["doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/PreferenceKey"]},{"title":"Storage","anchor":"Storage","identifiers":["doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/PreferenceValues"]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/tuikit\/preferences"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"API Collection","title":"Preferences","role":"collectionGroup","modules":[{"name":"TUIkit"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit\/Preferences","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/TUIkit\/documentation\/TUIkit"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TUIkit’s preference system enables "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bottom-up data flow"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the reverse of environment values. While the environment passes data down from parent to child, preferences let child views publish values that ancestors can observe and react to."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The s